{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ec108d6d-1acc-41b0-ae54-89cf5b3a4af4","content":"Yes, you'll hit **target framework compatibility issues**. MSTest v3 drops support for:\n\n- **`net5.0`** — .NET 5 is out of support; you need **`net6.0`** or later.\n- **`net462`** — frameworks older than **.NET Framework 4.6.2** are dropped, but yours is exactly 4.6.2 so it's borderline — check whether the MSTest v3 package actually resolves for it (some builds require 4.7.2+).\n- **`netcoreapp3.1`** — also out of support and dropped in MSTest v3.\n\n**To migrate successfully**, update your `TargetFrameworks` to supported TFMs, e.g.:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFrameworks>net6.0;net472</TargetFrameworks>\n```\n\n(or `net8.0` if you can go newer).\n\nWould you like me to perform the full migration (update TFMs, upgrade packages, adopt MSTest v3 patterns)?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f5217ebd-5600-4faf-9743-af075d382e53","outputTokens":244,"requestId":"A425:3F1DAE:1477BB4:160B0A3:6A02EC53"},"id":"b29008d3-9151-462d-a0b8-9695f8273e9e","timestamp":"2026-05-12T09:01:15.902Z","parentId":"69cc8fd5-213a-4361-bce2-1ce2d04bd7e5"}
